data.description: End your home search with this stunning home newly constructed in 2023 nestled in the thriving 55+ community of Esplanade at Tradition. This turn-key upgraded Bergamo model features a beautiful open floor plan. You will love the 8' interior door package, wrap around cafe coastal kitchen with new stainless-steel appliances, white shaker cabinets, oversized quartz island, walk-in pantry, gas cooktop and wall oven, custom hood vent, and a tankless hot water heater. Step inside the spacious owner's suite to find a custom walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom which offers two vanities and a large shower. Down the hall you'll find a second bedroom, full bathroom, bonus den/flex room with glass pane French doors, and laundry room. Unwind and enjoy the fresh air on the extended screened lanai that overlooks a scenic preserve. The two-car garage and widened driveway offers ample space for parking. The home features impact windows and doors throughout. The community of Esplanade is truly a resort-inspired way of life, where every day feels like a vacation. Enjoy the nearly completed amenity package plan: on-site lifestyle manager, resort-style pool and spa, tennis, pickleball, bocce ball courts, state-of-the-art fitness center catering kitchen, massage treatment room, fireside seating, event lawn, pet park, and so much more. Welcome home!
